Provided Parameters

Name URI Descirption Access Mode
Premption Priority sdmmc004_irwinterruptpriority This sets the Preemption Priority for this module R/W
Sub Priority sdmmc004_irwinterruptsubpriority This sets the Sub Priority for this module. R/W
SDWC sdmmc004_write_protect This allows a user to choose the optional Write Protect signal. It should be selected only if kit has the support for this signal. R/W
SDCD sdmmc004_card_detection This allows a user to choose the optional Card Detection signal. It should be selected only if kit has the support for this signal. R/W
LED sdmmc004_led This allows a user to choose the optional LED signal. It should be selected only if kit has the support for this signal. R/W
Data Lines Configuration sdmmc004_use_4_data_lines This allows a user to select the number of Data Lines to use. 1 or 4 data lines can be selected. R/W
Reset Configuration sdmmc004_reset This allows user to set the SDMCMC Reset Signal when required in the board. By default Hw board supports SDMMC Reset Signal. R/W
Bus Power Configuration sdmmc004_bus_power This allows user to set the SDMCMC bus power as and when required in the board. By default Hw board supplies bus power. R/W
